\c 20
\s UAbrahama loAbhimeleki
\p
\v 1 UAbrahama wasesuka lapho waya elizweni leningizimu\x + \xt 18.1,33.\x*, wahlala phakathi kweKadeshi leShuri\x + \xt 16.7,14.\x* wahlala njengowezizwe\x + \xt 26.3.\x* eGerari\x + \xt 10.19; 26.6.\x*.
\v 2 UAbrahama wasesithi ngoSara umkakhe: Ungudadewethu\x + \xt 12.13-20; 26.7-11.\x*. UAbhimeleki inkosi yeGerari wathuma-ke, wathatha uSara.
\v 3 Kodwa uNkulunkulu weza\x + \xt Hlab. 105.14.\x* kuAbhimeleki ephutsheni\x + \xt Jobe 33.15,16.\x* ebusuku, wathi kuye: Khangela, ufile\x + \xt 20.7.\x* ngenxa yowesifazana omthetheyo, ngoba uganile endodeni.
\v 4 Kodwa uAbhimeleki wayengasondelanga kuye. Ngakho wathi: Nkosi, uzabhubhisa lesizwe esilungileyo\x + \xt 18.23.\x* yini?
\v 5 Kayisuye yini othe kimi: Ungudadewethu? Laye uqobo wasesithi: Ungumnewethu. Ngobuqotho benhliziyo yami langobuhlophe bezandla zami ngikwenzile lokhu.
\v 6 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuye ephutsheni: Lami sengazile ukuthi ngobuqotho benhliziyo yakho ukwenzile lokhu; lami futhi ngikuvimbele ukuze ungoni kimi\x + \xt 39.9. Hlab. 51.4.\x*; ngenxa yalokhu kangikuvumelanga ukuthi umthinte.
\v 7 Ngakho-ke buyisela umfazi wendoda, ngoba ingumprofethi; njalo izakukhulekela\x + \xt Eks. 7.1. 1 Sam. 7.5. Jobe 42.8.\x* ukuze uphile; kodwa uba ungambuyiseli, yazi ukuthi isibili uzakufa wena labo bonke abangabakho\x + \xt Nani 16.32,33.\x*.
\v 8 UAbhimeleki wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, wabiza zonke inceku zakhe, wakhuluma wonke lamazwi endlebeni zazo; njalo amadoda esaba kakhulu.
\v 9 UAbhimeleki wasembiza uAbrahama, wathi kuye: Wenzeni kithi? Ngoneni kuwe ukuthi ungilethele mina lombuso wami isono esikhulu? Wenze kimi izenzo ezingafanelanga ukwenziwa\x + \xt 29.26; 34.7.\x*.
\v 10 UAbhimeleki wasesithi kuAbrahama: Uboneni, uze wenze into le?
\v 11 UAbrahama wasesithi: Ngoba ngacabanga \add ukuthi\add*: Isibili ukwesaba uNkulunkulu kakukho kulindawo\x + \xt Zaga 16.6.\x*; njalo bazangibulala ngenxa yomkami.
\v 12 Kanti-ke isibili \add ung\add*udadewethu\x + \xt 11.29.\x*, uyindodakazi kababa, kodwa kasiyo indodakazi kamama; wasesiba ngumkami.
\v 13 Kwasekusithi mhla uNkulunkulu engizulisa ngisuka endlini kababa\x + \xt 12.1.\x* ngasengisithi kuye: Lo ngumusa ozawenza kimi, kuzo zonke indawo esizafika kuzo, uthi ngami: Ungumnewethu\x + \xt 12.13.\x*.
\v 14 UAbhimeleki wasethatha izimvu lezinkomo lezinceku lezincekukazi\x + \xt 12.16.\x*, wapha uAbrahama, wambuyisela uSara umkakhe.
\v 15 UAbhimeleki wasesithi: Khangela, ilizwe lami liphambi kwakho\x + \xt 13.9; 34.10.\x*; hlala lapho okuhle khona emehlweni akho.
\v 16 LakuSara wathi: Khangela, ngimnikile umnewenu\x + \xt 20.5.\x* inhlamvu zesiliva eziyinkulungwane; khangela, uyisisibekelo samehlo\x + \xt 24.65.\x* kuwe sawo wonke olawe, labo bonke, njalo ukhuziwe\x + \xt 21.25.\x*.
\p
\v 17 UAbrahama wasekhuleka kuNkulunkulu; uNkulunkulu wasemsilisa uAbhimeleki lomkakhe lencekukazi zakhe, ukuze bazale.
\v 18 Ngoba iN\sc KOSI\sc* yayizivalile ngokupheleleyo izizalo\x + \xt 12.17.\x* zonke zabendlu kaAbhimeleki ngenxa kaSara umkaAbrahama.
